	<summary>A simple bullet-dodging game</summary>

	<description>
		<p>A simple bullet-dodging game. Survive as long as possible.</p>
		<p>How to play:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Move: W/A/S/D</li>
			<li>Rotation: The airplane looks at the mouse position</li>
			<li>Attack: Keep left mouse button pressed down</li>
		</ul>
	</description>

